{"tid":2027783,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一線生機 建立以金本位的黃色現金券制度","createTime":"2020-05-21T13:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T12:22:38.000Z","uid":326037,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7d43c4e577a26c27b561459041b3dad0ae49cf","tid":2027783,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"設一個可買賣的海外基金買金銀ETF，以金本位發行黃色經濟圈現金券黎貿易如何?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOGkSCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOGkSCx.png&h=9090bfdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5913eb74f40011994c6a89ad162fed59b3a3414a","tid":2027783,"uid":51920,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"d 設計好似藍絲廢老圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b7414900312030ad0a65ad98b18f5069f42bc8","tid":2027783,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"(攬炒懶人包) 全民拎綜援 政府冇銀用<br />\n<br />\n政府冇銀用 一籌莫展 <br />\n<br />\n用盡每一個方法駛政府錢拉挎政府財政，有機會/合資格拎綜援的人可以試下申請 唔駛再怕人嫌棄<br />\n<br />\n搞到政府冇錢先係攬炒主要目標，冇錢就冇能力推行反人權的政治理念<br />\n<br />\n要贏就要大部分人不滿現狀必須包括政府，不必令其不滿你，只要令其不滿自己<br />\n<br />\n(攬炒公務員)政府冇錢比人工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒國企藍店)永續黃圈 民主消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒銀行)唔夠美金 大陸金融有流動性陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒流動支付)唔用支付寶吸唔到香港人血<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒金融流動性)冇美金印唔到錢借唔到出去救經濟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒人民幣)數碼人民幣買唔到外國貨只能國內消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n(反攻香港)建立海外武裝反政兼逃生 養流亡義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒經濟)數碼經濟轉型 反送中生機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒外史)全球最大全民抗極權經驗 波蘭反共運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請每日推一次"},{"pid":"6eca6a9db979dbd625122c6fb4f954e1e0e6496e","tid":2027783,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5913eb74f40011994c6a89ad162fed59b3a3414a","tid":2027783,"uid":51920,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"d 設計好似藍絲廢老圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呀"},{"pid":"6926c2ebe15f24ce733025c02a52476867e67b98","tid":2027783,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"邊個有足夠數量嘅黃金儲備做到依樣嘢？"},{"pid":"ddc8c3f409b1375395d56133c6e9e73edfb2082e","tid":2027783,"uid":1915,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"咩年代仲金本位"},{"pid":"5f8677dcf3421f44c0a7d740ef668b78e589ab63","tid":2027783,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eca6a9db979dbd625122c6fb4f954e1e0e6496e","tid":2027783,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5913eb74f40011994c6a89ad162fed59b3a3414a","tid":2027783,"uid